# Serena (agent LSP) per-worktree runtime scratch. The shared project config
# (.serena/project.yml, .serena/.gitignore) is already tracked and stays tracked;
# this only keeps regenerated/untracked Serena files (run-id project.yml, cache,
# memories) from being swept into commits by tooling that runs `git add -A`.
/.serena/
